{"word":"ἐκτός","slug":"ἐκτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκτός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐκ'><el>ἐκ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>outside</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>ἐντός</el>: <p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>as <a href='S:Preposition'><a href='S:Preposition'>prep.</a></a> with <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>outside, out of, far from</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>: <i>outside of, free from</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; <el>ἐκτὸς ἐλπίδος</el> <i>beyond</i> hope, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>praeter spem</el>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of Time, <i>beyond</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>except</i>, <el>ἐκτὸς ὀλίγων</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>τὰ ἐκτός</el> <i>external things</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>with Verbs of motion, <el>ρίπτειν ἐκτός</el> to throw <i>out</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}